import React from 'react'
import { Grid, Image } from 'semantic-ui-react'
import "../../styles/Dashboard.css";
import ChangableStatistic from './ChangableStatistic';
import TimeSerie from './charts/TimeSerie';

const Section = () => (
  <Grid className="section"  stackable columns="equal">
    <Grid.Row>
    <Grid.Column width={4}>
        <ChangableStatistic name="star" color="green" degreeOfChange={1.5} text="Cookie Sold" label="today"/>
        <ChangableStatistic name="thumbs down" color="red" degreeOfChange={1.05} text="Cookie Wasted" label="today" />
      </Grid.Column>
      <Grid.Column width={8}>
        <TimeSerie />
      </Grid.Column>
    </Grid.Row>

    <Grid.Row>
      <Grid.Column width={4}>
      <ChangableStatistic name="thumbs down" color="red" degreeOfChange={1.05} text="Cookie Wasted" label="today" />
      </Grid.Column>
      <Grid.Column>
        <Image src='https://react.semantic-ui.com/images/wireframe/paragraph.png' />
      </Grid.Column>
    </Grid.Row>
  </Grid>
)

export default Section
